
		Composite Pattern = Organization of Objects

			Component------------                
				^				|					
	 Inheritance|		Loop	|
				|				|
			---------			|
			|		|			|Association
			|		|			|
			Leaf	Composite----
			
	* The Inheritance captures the commonality between the Leaf and The Composite.
	* The Association allows the organization of Objects.
	
	* Example:
	
			Expression-------------------               
				^						|				
	 Inheritance|				Loop	|
				|						|
		-------------					|
		|			|					|Association
		|			|					|
		Constant	BinaryExpression-----
						^							
			 Inheritance|				
						|
						Adder
						Subtracter
						Multiplier
						Divider